msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">Проверьте</emphasis> если ошибка уже есть в "
"&online_buglist_url; системе отслеживания ошибок."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:690
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you can't find this bug mentioned, please <emphasis role=\"bold"
#| "\">submit</emphasis> it into the bug tracker by clicking the "
#| "<guibutton>Submit New</guibutton> button in the bug-tracker window. "
